WEBVTT

00:07.231 --> 00:09.668
You took one of me best
whores for your private use.

00:09.733 --> 00:12.331
Every day she's not under
my roof costs me money.

00:17.365 --> 00:18.961
Wait, listen to me!

00:20.329 --> 00:23.503
Good men will die for some hidden agenda,

00:23.568 --> 00:25.533
the Barlow woman's agenda.

00:25.598 --> 00:28.265
Things will get better here.
I promise you they will.

00:28.330 --> 00:29.801
We'll need some additional items.

00:29.866 --> 00:31.738
New guns, 12-pounders.

00:31.803 --> 00:33.338
You'll have it.

00:33.403 --> 00:36.103
You want the guns from my
ship to hand over to a pirate?

00:36.176 --> 00:37.269
That is correct.

00:37.342 --> 00:38.635
Help me, Mr. Scott.

00:38.708 --> 00:40.335
Please, help me save her.

00:40.400 --> 00:41.597
Why don't I take over?

00:43.331 --> 00:44.769
The Andromache, it can't be.

00:44.834 --> 00:46.464
Captain Bryson hasn't had time to unload.

00:46.537 --> 00:48.134
He didn't. She's riding low.

00:48.199 --> 00:49.668
Those guns are still on board.

00:49.733 --> 00:51.966
- What are we going to do?
- Get them back.

